    <section_number>8</section_number>
    <catch_line>Uniforms</catch_line>
    <order_by>8</order_by>
    <text>
        Officers and employees in each such institution required to wear uniforms while on duty shall be furnished at the expense of the commonwealth with such uniforms of standard pattern as shall be prescribed by the commissioner.
